snippet.title: Deep Cuts - Launch Trailer | Play on Meta Quest 🎬
snippet.description:
Quest: https://www.meta.com/en-gb/experiences/6888594277865616/

Coming soon:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3035010/Deep_Cuts/

It’s time for your starring role in Deep Cuts – a genre-bending blend of messy physics, rich storytelling, and highly detailed worlds. A new chapter in the Scythe Saga Universe from the horror masterminds behind Happy's Humble Burger Farm!

Take on the role of Elise Weber, co-founder of film production studio Lights Camera Faction, as they embark on a blockbuster quest to save their best friend and creative partner, Malcolm Micheaux, by venturing through the duo’s expansive film catalog. 

*********

Follow our socials or join the Deep Cuts community 👇
Discord: discord.gg/happyshumble
Twitter (X):  https://x.com/DeepCuts_Game
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/deepcutsgame/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@lightscamerafaction
